msgstr "由支持能力和可选已审阅草稿组装一个本地工作台制品；它不会写入文章正文。"

msgid "Governed Handoffs"
msgstr "治理交接"

msgid "Reviewed Draft Handoff"
msgstr "已审阅草稿交接"

msgid "Prepare a Core-ready article_write_plan only after a human-reviewed draft exists. Toolbox does not submit or approve the proposal."
msgstr "仅在已有人工审阅草稿后准备 Core 就绪的 article_write_plan。Toolbox 不提交或审批提案。"

